{"word":"ὑπολύω","slug":"ὑπολύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n108740\" key=\"u(polu/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὑπολύω</orth>, <sense id=\"n108740.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">loosen beneath</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">below,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπέλυσε δὲ γυῖα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">made</tr_> his limbs <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">give way under him</tr_> (by giving him a deadly wound), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:581\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.581</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πολλῶν ἀνδρῶν ὑπὸ γούνατ᾽ ἔλυσε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:236\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.236</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπέλυσε μένος καὶ φαίδιμα γυῖα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">made</tr_> courage and strength <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fail,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.27</biblScope> </bibl>; of wrestlers, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑπέλυσε δὲ γυῖα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:726\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.726</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><