2</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg008.perseus-grc1:1183\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1183</biblScope> </bibl>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">take off one's own</tr_> sandals or shoes, or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">have</tr_> them <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">taken off,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὰς ἐμβάδας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:1157\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1157</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (prob. cj. for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑποδύου</foreign>): abs., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπολύεσθαι,</foreign> opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑποδεῖσθαι,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg007.perseus-grc1:950\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">950</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg011.perseus-grc1:927\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">927</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:4:5:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScop